WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.760
Wait, uh, the bill, please.

2
00:00:01.760 --> 00:00:04.240
Oh, no need to pay. We can lead directly.

3
00:00:04.240 --> 00:00:06.320
You can't just dine and dash.

4
00:00:06.320 --> 00:00:08.160
A gentleman can't let Lady pay.

5
00:00:08.160 --> 00:00:10.240
But you're a tour guide.

6
00:00:10.240 --> 00:00:12.000
I mean, money isn't easy.

7
00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:13.679
Look, I'll pay this time.

8
00:00:13.679 --> 00:00:16.719
Come on, I want to go make a wish at the statue.

9
00:00:16.719 --> 00:00:25.500
Let's go.

10
00:00:25.500 --> 00:00:28.140
Legend says if you offer a coin to the statue,

11
00:00:28.140 --> 00:00:31.309
close your eyes, and you open them,

12
00:00:31.309 --> 00:00:59.390
you'll see your Mr. Right.

13
00:00:59.390 --> 00:01:01.049
Do you know them?

14
00:01:01.049 --> 00:01:03.729
My ex-boyfriend and his mistress.

15
00:01:03.729 --> 00:01:06.489
This place isn't magical anymore.

16
00:01:06.489 --> 00:01:20.540
Let's go.

17
00:01:20.540 --> 00:01:21.540
Be careful.

18
00:01:21.540 --> 00:01:24.659
OK.

19
00:01:24.659 --> 00:01:26.579
Be careful when you go back.

